summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a franchise from King County to construct, maintain and operate a water transmission pipeline over, across and along portions of 146th Avenue Southeast, Southeast 42nd Place, 145th Avenue Southeast and Newport Way between SR 90 and the Eastgate Reservoir, as therein more particularly set forth, for the 150th Avenue Southeast, et al, Pipeline project, and authorizing and directing the Superintendent of Water to sign said franchise for and on behalf of the City of Seattle.
